title: Total Uninstall 4.9.0.601 - SeraHQ.rar
description:
Total Uninstall helps you monitor any changes that are made to your system during installation of a new software product allowing you to perform a complete uninstall without having to rely on the supplied uninstall program (which may leave files or changes behind).

To use it, you simply launch the installation program from the Total Uninstall interface and select the system areas to be monitored.
